name: Experiment Or Die #40
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. As I stare at this design I wonder when — how many months or years from now — will the average person utter these words about the Crypto space? Time is hyper-condensed in this world and when the time finally comes it might seem like a century ago that I made it. It would be nice if I could look upon this work on some kind of futuristic wall monitor inside a gallery with my still living parents in the year 2043, and hear them utter "This is Real". Twitter and IG: Nikejerk.
